          <span class="bf-item-sci">(Clostridium scindens)</span>
          <span class="bf-item-desc">高脂飲食導致此菌增生，造成肝臟發炎與纖維化。</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bf-bact-slot bf-bact-bad-3 bad">
